{"tid":2336091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可能香港人都需要佢呢種精神","createTime":"2020-12-22T10:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T10:46:20.000Z","uid":381069,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a2467cb35f55f9e42f8674aaba0875a3d769c122","tid":2336091,"uid":381069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h2JO2-607Ic\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh2JO2-607Ic&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=082ae98f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h2JO2-607Ic</a><br />\n<br />\n佢靚仔？ 比佢靚仔嘅一啲都唔少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔熟佢，你頂多知佢係正能量撚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講，一開始淨係以為佢係一個過氣歌手<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但唔講真係唔知佢一路行過黎係咁難<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pDxzp-cCNhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpDxzp-cCNhk&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c98c1d43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pDxzp-cCNhk</a><br />\n<br />\n單親，公屋，貧窮，讀唔成書，好不容易因為音樂生命光明左左少少，但喺屋企又受到咁大打擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我更欣賞嘅係就算係佢咁都仍然可以咁有 heart 行落去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢唔靚仔，但我會記得佢個笑容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n比佢唱得好嘅都唔少，但我會記得佢把聲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p_95dJDhkUc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp_95dJDhkUc&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=37746130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p_95dJDhkUc</a><br />\n<br />\n你未必記得佢個名，但係你可能聽過佢首歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcpmnCP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcpmnCP.jpg&h=9e9e8aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老實講我唔覺得你會攞到冠軍，甚至三甲都唔得，但睇完你個故事我點可以唔 respect 你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5b60ed7e76e22c5aa8b588538a4b48b1f85347","tid":2336091,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T10:46:20.000Z","msg":"借個位宣傳下活動：<br />\n<br />\n快d入黎平安夜活動頻道!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2336042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2336042</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}